data.meta_description: Andrew Lewis is a sailboat racer who has competed for Trinidad and Tobago. He competed at the 2012, 2016, and 2020 Summer Olympic Games.
data.text:
Andrew Lewis is a sailboat racer who has competed for Trinidad and Tobago. He competed at the 2012, 2016, and 2020 Summer Olympic Games.
